title: Age of Rivals v3.13
description: Deep civilization-building strategy in a fast-paced card game.You know those games where you spend 10 hours building up a huge civilization with a carefully balanced economy, military, culture and defense so you can prove that you are the greatest ruler ever?  Age of Rivals is like a 10 minute version of that.
